ActParliament of Canada Act
SubjectMembers of the House of Commons to be Parliamentary Secretary to the Ministers ** Appointment **
PrecisOrder (1) terminating the appointments made by Order in Council P.C. 2019-1391 of December 11, 2019; and (2) appointing, for the period ending on February 12, 2021, certain Members of the House of Commons to be Parliamentary Secretary to the Ministers.
